Kristy McNichol https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kristy_McNichol 0 Christina Ann McNichol (born September 11, 1962) is an American actress and singer.She is known for such roles as Angel in the film Little Darlings, Polly in the film Only When I Laugh, and Barbara Weston in the TV sitcom Empty Nest. McNichol won two Emmy Awards for her portrayal of the teenaged daughter Letitia "Buddy" Lawrence in the TV drama series Family.
